title: Samsung Galaxy A73 is now available for pre-order in India
content:
The Samsung Galaxy A73 is now available for pre-order in India. Quitely launched alongside the Galaxy A53 last month, the Galaxy A73 is the most powerful smartphone in the Galaxy A series.
